TY  - JOUR
TI  - The One-Stage Deformation Method: An Algorithm for Quadratic Programming
AU  - Bove, Roger Even
AB  - [This paper presents a considerably abbreviated deformation method for the minimization of a quadratic function subject to linear constraints. In Section 1 the method is explained for a positive definite function. In Section 2 it is extended to singular forms.]
