TI  - Solutions to the Decomposable von Neumann Model
AU  - Weil, Roman L.
AB  - [A method is shown for finding all solutions to the generalized von Neumann model formulated by Kemeny, Morgenstern, and Thompson. The method uses results from decomposing economic production systems to extend the algorithm of Hamburger, Thompson, and Weil.]
